OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fvariable amounts of cloud, most
OL,7,Fpersistent in the far west. Strong and
OL,8,Fgusty winds around coasts and over the
OL,9,FMoors. Chilliest in the east where
OL,10,Fwinds are lightest, with pockets of
OL,11,Fgrass frost possible in sheltered
OL,12,Frural areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FStrong winds on Wednesday
OL,15,Fwith gales possible near exposed
OL,16,Fcoasts and hills. Sunshine turning
OL,17,Fhazier through the day as cloud
OL,18,Fbuilds, with a chance of showers in
OL,19,Fthe far west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
