OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,FThursday and Friday with high pressure
OL,7,Fdominating. Often sunny and feeling
OL,8,Fwarm by day. Chilly nights as winds
OL,9,Fslowly ease. Cloudier on Saturday with
OL,10,Fa chance of rain.
